getRandomSolution(Problem) - Static method in class modelP.JSSP
Returns a two dimensional integer array representation of a solution
The array is of size [m][j] where m is the number of machines in the problem and j is the number of jobs
For each machine 0 to m-1 the array holds the order that jobs should be processes on that machine
